58
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:42,260
Well, as I said, we're going to start a series in two weeks

59
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:45,820
called Tough Questions and Honest Answers.

60
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:48,840
Because I know there are still, for many people,

61
